---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: "Superannuation Minimum Drawdowns in Australia (2026 Guide)",
  description: "Comprehensive guide to Australian Superannuation Account-Based Pensions, statutory minimum drawdown percentage rates by age, condition of release rules, and tax-free status after age 60.",
  schema: `
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Article",
        "headline": "Superannuation Minimum Drawdowns in Australia",
        "author": {
          "@type": "Person",
          "name": "Mrittunjoy Das"
        },
        "publisher": {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "name": "TaxDebtWealthSuite"
        },
        "datePublished": "2026-07-23",
        "dateModified": "2026-07-23",
        "description": "Comprehensive guide to Australian Superannuation Account-Based Pensions, statutory minimum drawdown percentage rates by age, and tax-free status."
      }
    </script>
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "FAQPage",
        "mainEntity": [
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What is the minimum drawdown percentage for an Australian Account-Based Pension?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "For ages 65–74, the minimum annual drawdown is 5% of account balance as of July 1. For ages 75–79 it rises to 6%, ages 80–84 to 7%, ages 85–89 to 9%, ages 90–94 to 11%, and 95+ to 14%."
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    </script>
  `
};
---

<Layout title={seo.title} description={seo.description} head={seo.schema}>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <header class="mb-12 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest border border-emerald-500/20 mb-6">
        <span>Australia Super Drawdown</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
        Superannuation Minimum Drawdowns in Australia
      </h1>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Mrittunjoy+Das&background=00F5D4&color=000" alt="Mrittunjoy Das" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full" />
          By <span class="text-white font-medium">Mrittunjoy Das</span>
        </span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time datetime="2026-07-23">July 23, 2026</time>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Embedded Calculator Callout Banner -->
    <div class="my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[#141C32] to-[#1E294B] border border-[#00F5D4]/30 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div class="space-y-1">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#00F5D4] uppercase tracking-wider">Interactive Tool</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Australia Super Minimum Drawdown Calculator</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">Calculate ATO Account-Based Pension minimum annual drawdown rates by age bracket.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/superannuation-rrsp-withdrawal-calculator/australia/" class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-[#00F5D4] hover:bg-[#00F5D4]/90 text-slate-950 font-bold text-xs whitespace-nowrap transition-all shadow-lg shadow-[#00F5D4]/20">
        Estimate AU Drawdown →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        The Australian Superannuation system requires APRA-regulated funds and Self-Managed Super Funds (SMSFs) to enforce statutory minimum annual drawdown limits once a member transfers their accumulation account into an <strong>Account-Based Pension (ABP)</strong>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">1. ATO Statutory Minimum Payment Standards</h2>
      <p>
        Statutory minimum drawdowns scale by age: &lt;65 (4%), 65–74 (5%), 75–79 (6%), 80–84 (7%), 85–89 (9%), 90–94 (11%), and 95+ (14%).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">Related Calculators & Strategy Guides</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6">
        <a href="/superannuation-rrsp-withdrawal-calculator/australia/" class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 hover:border-[#00F5D4]/40 transition-all space-y-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#00F5D4] uppercase">Calculator</span>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Super Drawdown Tool</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Calculate ATO minimum pension drawdowns.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/rmd-calculator/australia/" class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-500/40 transition-all space-y-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-400 uppercase">Related Tool</span>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">RMD Calculator</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Model Account-Based Pension minimums.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/roth-conversion-calculator/" class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 hover:border-amber-500/40 transition-all space-y-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-amber-400 uppercase">Related Tool</span>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Roth Conversion Calculator</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Model global tax-bracket conversion strategies.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
